SUB_W04_EVAR_MIDO_BASE_START_PROCESS_000.text:
That sounds about right to me, guy;
wishes come at a cost, and the bigger
the wish, the higher the price.

SUB_W04_EVAR_MIDO_BASE_STORM_CENTER_000_.text:
Deus Maris's a big fan of you, Cap'n;
it's like the cyclone appeared just to
give you back the egg.

SUB_W04_EVAR_MIDO_BASE_NORTHHARBOR_WORLD.text:
Baltasar's not a man to forget a grudge;
he's probably going to want to string
me up while he plays the hornpipe.

SUB_W04_EVAR_MIDO_PIRATESHIP_BIRD_QUEST_.text:
Yar, I suppose ya be but a victim;
'tis the fault of that slimy eel, Sigurd.
Here, cully. The treasure be yours.

SUB_W04_EVAR_MIDO_GHOSTSHIP_LASTBATTLE_1.text:
Ah. It seems the wish comes with a price;
I cannot be freed from my burden until I
bring down this fiend.
